These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: disaster, musical, romance, sports, superhero
The people use 5 different means of transport: subway, skateboard, scooter, ship, bike
1. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
4. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
6. the person watching disaster movies is in the middle##1
7. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical | romance | disaster | superhero | sports |
| Transport   | bike    | subway | scooter     | ship       | skateboard  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-2::.
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: june, february, october, january, july
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: disco, indie, metal, r&b, rock
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the fan of indie##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
4. the person who's birthday is in june is in the middle##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is the fan of metal##1
6. the fan of rock is the person who's birthday is in july##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |      3      |    4     |   5    |
| Birthday      | february | october | june | january | july |
| Music-Genre   | metal  | r&b   | disco       | indie    | rock   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-3::.
There 5 different types of food: apricot, garlic, kale, nectarine, raspberry
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: december, february, september, july, august
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
3. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
4. the person eating kale is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
6. the person eating garlic is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |     2     |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Food        | kale | nectarine | garlic | apricot | raspberry |
| Birthday   | february  | december      | august | september | july      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-4::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daffodil, lily, aconite, poppy, sunflower
The people have 5 different jobs:  fisherman, nurse, paramedic, social-worker, writer
1. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the nurse##1
2. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the nurse##1
3. the social-worker is on the right of the fisherman##1
4. the person who growslily is on the right of the writer##1
5. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
6. the paramedic is on the far right##1
7. the writer is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |    3    |    4    |     5     |
| Flower   | poppy    | daffodil        | aconite | lily | sunflower |
| Job     | fisherman | social-worker | writer  | nurse   | paramedic |

