.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-5::.
There 5 different types of food: banana, cherry, grapes, mango, strawberry
There are 5 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water, milk, sprite, tea
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
2. the person drinking water is the person eating strawberry##1
3. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating banana##1
6. the person drinking tea is the person eating mango##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3     |       4       |     5      |
| Food    | grapes   | banana     | cherry   | mango         | strawberry |
| Beverage   | lemonade | sprite | milk | tea | water     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, cricket, handball, volleyball
5 different games are played: chess, monopoly, snooker, go, domino
1. the person playing go is in the middle##1
2. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
3. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person playing go##1
4. the person playing snooker is the person who's sport is cricket##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |     5     |
| Sport       | handball   | cricket   | baseball | volleyball | badminton |
| Game   | monopoly | snooker | go   | domino | chess       |

