.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-7::.
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, pony, rabbit, rat
There 5 different types of food: apricot, spinach, kiwi, lettuce, grapes
1. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
2. the person eating apricot is the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
5. the person eating spinach is in the middle##1
6. the person eating kiwi is the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2   |    3     |     4      |     5      |
| Pet     | frog   | pony  | rat      | chinchilla | rabbit     |
| Food   | lettuce | kiwi | spinach | apricot   | grapes |

