.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-8::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  chef, engineer, manager, scientist, teacher
There are 5 different favourite colors: chestnut, azure, amber, yellow, orange
1. the person who likes orange is on the left of the teacher##1
2. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1
4. the teacher is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
5. the person who likes azure is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
6. the chef is on the right of the engineer##1
7. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |
| Job     | engineer | chef       | teacher | scientist | manager    |
| Color   | yellow   | orange | amber  | azure     | chestnut |

