.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-9::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: camping, dancing, magic-tricks, photography, woodworking
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, cain, prince, havana, swisher
1. the prince-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
5. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the cain-smoker##1
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the cain-smoker##1
7. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |      3       |      4      |    5    |
| Hobby         | photography | camping | magic-tricks | woodworking | dancing |
| Cigar   | prince       | havana   | swisher         | cain   | old-henry   |

