1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the owner of the frog is the person who growssunflower##1
4. the person who growslily is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the goldfish is in the middle##1
6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |    4    |    5     |
| Flower   | iris | lily | orchid | marigold | sunflower |
| Pet           | rat      | fish    | goldfish  | dog     | frog     |

