.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: parkour, ice-hockey, handball, rugby, sailing
5 different pets are kept: cat, dog, goat, rabbit, snake
1. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
2. the owner of the dog is the person who's sport is rugby##1
3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
5. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1
6. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
7. the owner of the snake is the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |   2    |    3    |     4     |      5      |
| Sport   | rugby | parkour  | handball | ice-hockey | sailing |
| Pet    | dog    | rabbit | snake   | cat       | goat        |

