.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-13::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, iris, rose, balloon-flower, marigold
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, subway, train, tram
1. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the subway is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who growsamaryllis##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is the person driving the subway##1
5. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who growsamaryllis##1
6. the person who growsballoon-flower is in the middle##1
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |    3    |    4     |    5    |
| Flower   | rose | amaryllis      | balloon-flower | iris | marigold |
| Transport     | train  | snowmobile | bus     | tram     | subway  |

