.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-14::.
The people have 5 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, electrician, dancer, firefighter
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, dutch, indonesian, mexican, turkish
1. the dressmaker is on the right of the turkish##1
2. the coach is in the middle##1
3. the mexican is on the right of the dutch##1
4. the electrician is on the left of the coach##1
5. the electrician is on the left of the argentine##1
6. the dancer is on the right of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |    4     |     5      |
| Job      | firefighter | electrician | coach      | dancer | dressmaker      |
| Nationality   | dutch  | mexican       | argentine | turkish  | indonesian |

