4. the pall-mall-smoker is the nurse##1
5. the engineer is on the far right##1
6. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the nurse##1
7. the swisher-smoker is on the left of the accountant##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |     3      |   4    |    5     |
