.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-16::.
There 5 different types of food: apricot, asparagus, blueberry, lime, peach
There are 5 different favourite colors: lilac, turquise, amber, green, ebony
1. the person eating peach is on the left of the person eating apricot##1
2. the person eating lime is on the far right##1
3. the person eating apricot is the person who likes turquise##1
4. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who likes green##1
5. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
6. the person who likes amber is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |      5      |
| Food    | asparagus   | blueberry | peach      | apricot | lime        |
| Color   | ebony | lilac     | amber | turquise | green |

