.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-19::.
5 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hedgehog, snake, dog, lizard
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, cricket, handball, surfing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
2. the owner of the dog is on the far right##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left##1
4. the person who's sport is handball is the owner of the dog##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
7. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's sport is basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |   4    |    5     |
| Pet   | lizard     | snake       | chinchilla     | hedgehog  | dog  |
| Sport      | surfing | basketball | cricket | tennis | handball |

