.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, romance, satire, thriller
The people have 5 different hobbies: reading, fishing, gardening, camping, sudoku
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is in the middle##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
6. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the person watching romance movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2     |    3    |      4      |   5    |
| Movie-Genre   | drama | thriller | romance | documentary | satire |
| Hobby           | sudoku | camping  | fishing    | reading  | gardening   |

 